Meet your newest Lake Dallas residents and first time home buyers! 

I’m so stinkin proud of us! We’ve worked so  incredibly hard for this! To finally have the keys in hand is such a gratifying feeling. 

Rebeca is my world and I can’t wait to start building on to our amazing collection of memories in this home. Another stepping stone is down in our life together, and what a life it is. 

Of course, this wouldn’t have been possible without our Realtor, Claudia and our Lender, Josh. This is not a sales pitch at all… BUT, I cannot stress enough how important it is to have a realtor and lender that legitimately CARE about you throughout the process. Josh and Claudia seriously worked so hard on our behalf. They have an incredible amount of knowledge, as well as patience and always made sure we knew every single step we needed to take. I cannot recommend these two enough! 

“Chance residents, this is Sam speaking.”

Congratulations to Lane + Avery! ♥️ They are SO beautiful together. We feel so lucky to have the chance to be there and capture it ALL!♥️ Full video coming soon. 🎥 #dallasvideographer #weddingproduction #wedding #love #weddingvideography #weddingvideographer #dfwvideographer

Celebrating a Year of Love and Laughter with my best friend! ⁣
⁣
Today, we mark a special milestone - Beca's very first birthday as my beautiful wife.  From the moment we said "I do," life has been a breathtaking adventure filled with love, laughter, and endless joy.⁣
⁣
Beca, you are my light that brightens every day, and your smile can chase away any storm. Your kindness, grace, and unwavering support continue to amaze me. ⁣
⁣
This year, we've shared unforgettable moments, created lasting memories, and navigated life's twists and turns together. Whether it's a cozy evening watching tv, shooting video, or playing with our fur babies, every moment with you is so special. ⁣
⁣
Your love is the compass that guides me through life's journey, and I am endlessly grateful for the privilege of being your husband. As we enter your 27th year together, I can't wait to see all the beautiful moments and memories we'll create.⁣
⁣
Happy birthday, my love! May this day be filled with all the joy and happiness you bring to my life every day. Here's to many more birthdays, laughter, and love together. ❤️ @missrebeca

1 year ago today I married my best friend. I’m so proud of our relationship and the castle we are building. I am beyond thankful for all of the lessons we have learned in our first year of marriage. ⁣
⁣
The Lord blessed me with such an amazing woman and I will forever be grateful. ⁣
⁣
Happy Anniversary Rebeca ❤️
